The Mannasim Framework - Source Code distribution
-----------------------

To install Mannasim Framework source code distribution just follows the steps
presented bellow:

1. Get ns-2.29 all-in-one package from ns-2 site. 

2. Get MannaSim Framework tar.gz file.

3. Unpack the tar.gz file into ns-2.29 main folder (if using ns all-in-one 
distribution ns-allinone-2.29/ns-2.29 folder). Inside mannasim/ folder just 
created look for a ns-modified-files/ folder where ns-2.29 modified files are
stored.

4. Substitue ns-2.29 files listed bellow by it's MannaSim version
stored in ns-modified-files/ folder in mannasim/ directory.

- ns-2.29/apps/udp.cc
- ns-2.29/common/ns-process.h
- ns-2.29/common/packet.cc
- ns-2.29/common/packet.h
- ns-2.29/mac/mac-802_11.cc
- ns-2.29/tcl/lib/ns-lib.tcl
- ns-2.29/tcl/lib/ns-default.tcl
- ns-2.29/Makefile.in

5. In ns-2.29 main folder re-run configuration script and then re-compile the
system:

./configure
./make


6. Files provided within source code distribution. 

- accessPointApp.cc
- accessPointApp.h
- aggregateProcessing.cc
- aggregateProcessing.h
- battery.cc
- battery.h
- carbonMonoxideAppData.cc
